The paper deals with the combinatorial and algorithmic aspects of planar graphs and their duals, which are topics that are typically studied in the sub-categories of Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Computational Geometry (cs.CG), and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS). The paper also involves graph theory (cs.GT) and complexity theory (cs.CC) in its algorithmic results.
